Most adverbs are morphologically either sti-derivations of adjectives or
some specific form of an existing or archaic noun, and they have limited
inflection in form of possessives and clitics carried over.

* __edessäni__

* __takanani__

* __takanaan__

* __jalkeilleen__

* __keskelleen__

* __edessään__

* __nopeastihan__

* __tyhmästihän__













